accessibility.text: I realised that a clear connection between user actions and the visuals displayed on screen was missing. Even if the potential was extensive, the overall experience was fragmented and unglued.  The excitement for the disruptive technology was undermined by a poor user experience
I am a strong ambassador of the UDC approach. I wanted to understand the user expectations and needs and determine a better experience. Hence I exploded the user journey and analysed each step.
You’ve got question. Voice has answers
After using it, did you get excited?
B. Is ok, but it could have been better
